  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the bottom of a clay or ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Brown the lamb shoulder on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the Algerian spice blend, cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the tagine sauce and bring to a simmer.",
    "Cover the tagine and cook over low heat for 2-3 hours, or until the lamb is tender.",
    "Serve hot with couscous and garnish with fresh herbs, if desired."
